1 //Namespace
  2 var EarthServerGenericClient = EarthServerGenericClient || {};
  3 
  4 EarthServerGenericClient.AnnotationLayer = function(Name,root,fontSize,fontColor,fontHover,markerSize,markerColor)
  5 {
  6     this.name = Name;
  7     var annotationTransforms = [];
  8 
  9     this.addAnnotation = function(xPos,yPos,zPos,Text)
 10     {
 11         for(var i=0;i<2;i++)
 12         {
 13             var textTransform = document.createElement('transform');
 14             textTransform.setAttribute('scale', fontSize + " " + fontSize + " " + fontSize);
 15             var shape = document.createElement('shape');
 16             var appearance = document.createElement('appearance');
 17             appearance.setAttribute("id","Layer_Appearance_"+Name);
 18             var material = document.createElement('material');
 19             material.setAttribute('emissiveColor', fontColor);
 20             material.setAttribute('diffuseColor', fontColor);
 21             var text = document.createElement('text');
 22             text.setAttribute('string', Text);
 23             var fontStyle = document.createElement('fontStyle');
 24             fontStyle.setAttribute('family', 'calibri');
 25             fontStyle.setAttribute('style', 'bold');
 26             text.appendChild(fontStyle);
 27             appearance.appendChild(material);
 28             shape.appendChild(appearance);
 29             shape.appendChild(text);
 30             textTransform.appendChild(shape);
 31 
 32             if(i===0)
 33             {
 34                 var sphere_trans = document.createElement("Transform");
 35                 sphere_trans.setAttribute("scale",markerSize + " " + markerSize + " "+markerSize);
 36                 sphere_trans.setAttribute('translation', xPos + " " + yPos + " " + zPos);
 37                 var sphere_shape = document.createElement("Shape");
 38                 var sphere = document.createElement("Sphere");
 39                 var sphere_app = document.createElement("Appearance");
 40                 var sphere_material = document.createElement('material');
 41                 sphere_material.setAttribute('diffusecolor', markerColor);
 42                 sphere_app.appendChild(sphere_material);
 43                 sphere_shape.appendChild(sphere_app);
 44                 sphere_shape.appendChild(sphere);
 45                 sphere_trans.appendChild(sphere_shape);
 46 
 47                 root.appendChild(sphere_trans);
 48                 annotationTransforms.push(sphere_trans);
 49 
 50                 sphere_trans = null;
 51                 sphere_shape = null;
 52                 sphere = null;
 53                 sphere_app = null;
 54                 sphere_material = null;
 55             }
 56 
 57             var rootTransform = document.createElement('transform');
 58 
 59             textTransform.setAttribute('translation', xPos + " " + (yPos+fontHover) + " " + zPos);
 60             textTransform.setAttribute('scale', (-fontSize) + " " + (-fontSize) + " " + fontSize);
 61 
 62             if(i===0)
 63             {
 64                 textTransform.setAttribute('rotation', '0 0 1 3.14');
 65             }
 66             else
 67             {
 68                 textTransform.setAttribute('rotation', '0 0 1 3.14');
 69                 textTransform.setAttribute('translation', -xPos + " " + (yPos+fontHover) + " " + -zPos);
 70                 rootTransform.setAttribute('rotation', '0 1 0 3.14');
 71             }
 72 
 73 
 74             annotationTransforms.push(rootTransform);
 75             rootTransform.appendChild(textTransform);
 76             root.appendChild( rootTransform );
 77         }
 78 
 79         textTransform = null;
 80         shape = null;
 81         appearance = null;
 82         material = null;
 83         text = null;
 84         fontStyle = null;
 85     };
 86 
 87     this.renderLayer = function( value )
 88     {
 89         for(var i=0; i<annotationTransforms.length;i++)
 90         {
 91             annotationTransforms[i].setAttribute("render",value);
 92         }
 93     };
 94 };
